name: Camp Nano 22 Rack Pack Carabiners (6 Pack)
description: A half-sack of wire gate carabiners with an unbeatable strength-to-weight ratio. They'll keep your rack light and your clips speedy.Relatively stiff wire won't rub open.Deep basket keeps the rope seated.Small proportions may not suit climbers with meaty fingers wearing big gloves.Dimensions are 8.5cm long by 4.5cm wide.
